OL,3,CSix dead after shooting in northern
OL,4,CGermany, police say
OL,6,FA shooting at a youth welfare facility
OL,7,Fin northern Germany on Mondayleft six
OL,8,Fpeople dead in what officials believe
OL,9,Fmay have stemmed from a custody
OL,10,Fdispute.JThe main suspect has been
OL,11,Farrested.
OL,13,FFive people ` four women and one man `
OL,14,Fdied at the scene of the shooting in
OL,15,FStade, police said. A sixth, also an
OL,16,Fadult, died later at a hospital. All
OL,17,Fsix were employees of the youth center
OL,18,For its affiliates, they said.
