OL,3,CSix dead after shooting in northern
OL,4,CGermany, police say
OL,6,F"The police are investigating the
OL,7,Fmotive and the exact course of events
OL,8,Funder high pressure," Daniela Behrens,
OL,9,Finterior minister for the Lower Saxony
OL,10,Fregion, told a news conference, adding
OL,11,Fthat it was an extremely violent crime
OL,12,Fin cold blood, "apparently in a
OL,13,Fcustody dispute."
OL,15,FPolice said the shooting took place
OL,16,Fnear a youth facility, prompting a
OL,17,Fmajor police operation on
OL,18,FDankersstrasse, south of the town
OL,19,Fcentre.
