OL,3,CSix dead after shooting in northern
OL,4,CGermany, police say
OL,6,FPosting on social media platform X,
OL,7,FLuneburg Police said "an operation is
OL,8,Fcurrently taking place in Stade" and
OL,9,Fthat members of the public should
OL,10,Favoid the area.
OL,12,FStade is a town located around 40
OL,13,Fkilometers west of Hamburg with a
OL,14,Fpopulation of around 50,000 people.
OL,16,FAn investigation is ongoing. Police
OL,17,Fsay there is "no danger to the public."
